      </div>
      <div class="principle">
        <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart"></i>
        <h3>Reader-Funded</h3>
        <p>No corporate sponsors dictate what we write. Readers who value quality content sustain our work.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="principle">
        <i class="fas fa-globe-asia"></i>
