  </section>

  <section class="timeline">
    <div class="section-head">
      <h2>Our journey</h2>
      <span>A short history</span>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline-list">
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-year">2026</div>
        <div>
          <h3>The BlogPost launches</h3>
          <p>A small team of writers leaves traditional media to create an independent blog focused on quality over quantity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-year">2026</div>
        <div>
          <h3>Reader community reaches 10,000</h3>
          <p>Direct reader support allows us to expand our coverage and bring on new voices.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
