          <h3>Global contributor network grows</h3>
          <p>We add writers from three new regions, bringing fresh perspectives to our blog.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="team">
    <div class="section-head">
      <h2>Our editorial team</h2>
      <span>The voices behind the words</span>
    </div>
    <div class="team-grid">
      <div class="team-card">
        <div class="avatar">EK</div>
        <h3>Elena Kwan</h3>
        <span class="role">Editor-in-Chief</span>
        <p>Oversees editorial quality and guides the blog's overall voice and direction.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="team-card">
        <div class="avatar">AO</div>
        <h3>Amara Okafor</h3>
        <span class="role">Senior Writer</span>
        <p>Leads long-form features and cultural commentary with depth and nuance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="team-card">
        <div class="avatar">RF</div>
        <h3>Rafael Ferreira</h3>
        <span class="role">Global Editor</span>
        <p>Manages international contributors and brings global perspectives to our blog.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="team-card">
        <div class="avatar">MS</div>
        <h3>Mei Suzuki</h3>
        <span class="role">Community Manager</span>
