  </section>

</div>


<div class="wrap">
  <section class="support">
    <h2>Support writing that answers only to its readers.</h2>
    <p>Become a member to fund independent blogging directly, or subscribe free to get our weekly digest in your inbox.</p>
    <div class="support-actions">
      <a href="signup.html"><button class="btn-primary">Become a member <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></button></a>
      <a href="index.html"><button class="btn-outline"><i class="fas fa-newspaper"></i> Read the latest posts</button></a>
